description:
The Dragon's Roar: Part 3 - An Old Testament story reveals how the devil attempts to prevent the latter rain and destroy Gods people; and how Christ outmaneuvers him bringing His tried and tested people through the fires and empowering them to give earths final warning. Presented by Tim Saxton, Associate Speaker for White Horse Media.
